column2: SELECT p.objId,p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.expAB_r,     p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i,      s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM galaxy AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid    JOIN galSpecInfo as g ON g.ra = p.ra AND g.dec = p.dec WHERE s.z between # and # ORDER BY p.objId
